        <div>
          <h1>Hello,</h1>
          <p>Welcome to our visitor management system. Check out our appointment scheduling and Upcoming events and make bookings at your own convenience.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img src="images/ill3.jpg" alt="guest" class="guest_ill">
