      <div class="updates">
        <div class="apt_cal_box">
          <h2>Appointment Calendar</h2>
          <p>This table entails the available time periods for guests or visitors to make appointments. The shceduling is universal for all departments.</p>
          
          <table class="calendar">
            <caption>
              Appointment Calendar
            </caption>
            <thead>
              <tr>
              <th>Monday</th>
              <th>Tuesday</th>
              <th>Wednesday</th>
              <th>Thursday</th>
              <th>Friday</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td data-cell="Monday">
                  <div>11:00am - 12:00pm</div>
                </td>
                <td data-cell="Tuesday">
                  <div>10:00am - 11:00am</div>
                </td>
                <td data-cell="Wednesday">
                  unavailable
                </td>
                <td data-cell="Thursday">
                  <div>2:00pm - 3:00pm</div>
                </td>
                <td data-cell="Friday">
                  unavailable
                </td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>

          <a href="/guestAps" class="btn btn_guest_sec">
            <span>
            <img style="width: 100%; background: transparent;" src="images/clock-file.svg" />
            </span>
            <span>Go to Appointments</span>
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="row_box events_box">
          <div>
            <h2>Upcoming Events</h2>
            
            <p>Using this platform to to to join events prior to when they're held helps us make plans of the respective events according to the number of participants.</p>
            <br/>
            <a href="/guestEvents" class="btn btn_guest_sec">
              <span>
                <img style="width: 100%; background: transparent;" src="images/submit.png" />
              </span>
              <span>Go to events</span>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div>
            <img src="images/ill1.jpg" alt="event"/>
          </div>
        </div>
        
      </div>
